nmetadata/org.bouncycastle/bcpkix-jdk18on/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.77\\\",\\nmetadata/org.bouncycastle/bcpkix-jdk15on/index.json:7:    \\\"metadata-version\\\": \\\"1.70\\\",\\nmetadata/org.jetbrains.exposed/exposed-jdbc/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.0.0\\\",\\nmetadata/org.apache.jackrabbit/jackrabbit-jcr-commons/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.5.0\\\",\\nmetadata/org.springframework/spring-instrument/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"5.3.31\\\",\\nmetadata/org.jetbrains.exposed/exposed-core/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.0.0-beta-4\\\",\\nmetadata/org.jetbrains.exposed/exposed-core/index.json:22:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.1.0\\\",\\nmetadata/org.jetbrains.exposed/exposed-core/index.json:40:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.0.0\\\",\\nmetadata/org.springframework/spring-aspects/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"5.3.31\\\",\\ndocs/CONTRIBUTING.md:99:* `metadata-version`: Specifies the subdirectory where the GraalVM configuration files (e.g., `reflect-config.json`) reside.\\ndocs/CONTRIBUTING.md:108:* `source-code-url`: URL to the metadata source code location for this index entry. Use `$version$` as the placeholder for this entry's `metadata-version` in versioned URLs.\\ndocs/CONTRIBUTING.md:110:* `test-code-url`: URL to the test source code location for this index entry. Use `$version$` as the placeholder for this entry's `metadata-version` in versioned URLs.\\ndocs/CONTRIBUTING.md:111:* `documentation-url`: URL to the project documentation for this index entry. Use `$version$` as the placeholder for this entry's `metadata-version` in versioned URLs.\\ndocs/CONTRIBUTING.md:122:    \\\"metadata-version\\\": \\\"1.0.0\\\",\\ndocs/CONTRIBUTING.md:138:     \\\"metadata-version\\\": \\\"1.1.0\\\",\\nmetadata/com.google.re2j/re2j/index.json:4:    \\\"metadata-version\\\" : \\\"1.1\\\",\\nmetadata/org.jetbrains.exposed/exposed-json/index.json:4:    \\